Rustenburg &#x2013; A toddler drowned after falling into a fishpond at her home in Morningside, Sandton north of Johannesburg on Wednesday, paramedics said.In a statement Netcare 911 said the little girl was declared dead at the scene by the provincial emergency services.&#x201C;When Netcare 911 paramedics arrived on scene, we found paramedics from the Provincial EMS already at the scene. Sadly, the little girl had already died. The toddler was declared dead on scene by paramedics from the Provincial EMS.&#x201D;Netcare 911 has called in one of its trauma counsellors to provide counselling to the distraught family. African News Agency